(1, 'Unko Sweater', 'unko-sweater', '2025', 'images/movies/movie_1770086802.jpg', 'The 2025 Nepali movie featuring the character Kafle is titled Unko Sweater (The Woolen Sweater). Directed by Nabin Chauhan and produced by Artmandu, the film stars Bipin Karki as Dharanidhar Kafle and Miruna Magar as Phool, portraying a romantic drama set in the eastern hills of Nepal.', '2026-02-02 15:16:42', '2026-02-02 15:16:42'),
(2, 'Furious 7', 'furious-7', '2015', 'images/movies/movie_1770116280.jpg', 'Furious 7 is a high-octane action film that follows Dominic Toretto and his crew as they face their most dangerous enemy yet Deckard Shaw, a ruthless assassin seeking revenge. Packed with intense car chases, explosive stunts, and global missions, the movie blends adrenaline-fueled action with strong themes of family, loyalty, and loss, making it one of the most emotional and memorable chapters in the Fast & Furious franchise.', '2026-02-03 10:58:00', '2026-02-03 10:58:00');
